microTiPi.microscopy

Class PSF_Estimation

  • java.lang.Object
    • microTiPi.microscopy.PSF_Estimation

  • public class PSF_Estimation
extends java.lang.Object
    Define a class for PSF estimation. This class contains all the parameters needed to estimate the PSF defined in the pupil property. The fit is performed using the fitPSF function.
